          "component_id": "story",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "artifactPos": "",
                "desc": "<p>Feeling defeated, it dawned on the Skyrider that there are things that swordsmanship cannot achieve.<br>So instead of believing in his swordsmanship, he turned to the sword itself.<br>\"Bigger is always better, and swords are no exception,\" he thought.<br>In the grand Guyun Stone Forest, he embraced his grand ending.<br>His dream of flight came to an end, but his sword and story would never fade...</p>",
                "id": "story58903",
                "img": "",
                "title": ""
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
